title: So What's Everyone Wearing to Rand Paul's Halloween Party?
text: Okay, it’s so annoying how there are like five different Halloween parties I have to go to, and I have to come up for a different costume for all of them, and one of them is all the way over in freaking Iowa but I feel like only a few people are going to show up and Republican presidential candidate Rand Paul will definitely be upset if I’m not there—are you guys going to go?
